➜三个五年，基本建成“美丽四川”
http://www.sohu.com/a/425810210_100148222	40836
<p><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201019/61b649e6fa524663ba8b8edf3ff9be90.jpeg" /></p>
<p>四川美不美丽？</p>
<p><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201019/b997c37e8bfa4b788ca19253fcd2bd62.png" /></p>
<p>当然美丽！</p>
<p><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201019/c7d3061c93bd4adcb188b42217259eca.png" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
